Package: signcon
Type: Package
Title: A Frequentist Statistical Framework to Test Weak, Nondirectional Null Hypotheses
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("M", "M", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "XXX"),
              person("Itay", "Yaron", role = "ctb", email = "mufc.itay@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: MM and IY <XX@XX.net>
Description: The goal of signcon is to provide a frequentist statistical framework to test a nondirectional null hypotheses. Nondirectional hypotheses may be rejected in cases where individual subjects show reliable effects, even if these effects have opposite signs and cancel out at the group level in a standard t-test. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
